An Alpha version of omnific.

It's been 11 years since omnifics release, so why not upload the original version of it?

This version has older stage designs & slight gameplay tweaks.

a18 = Alpha 18

This version was uploaded publicly to solidsurf in 2012, the leaked version of this map was b06, which I don't have, however, both b06 and a18 are very similiar.
